  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h1 id=\"RepairQ1.20.5.2-Bugs\">Bugs</h1><h3 id=\"RepairQ1.20.5.2-TicketsandTransactions\">Tickets and Transactions</h3><ul><li><p>Applying a Store Credit on a ticket no longer results in an error.</p></li><li><p>Resolved the issue causing broken images upon uploading a file to a Custom Form.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"RepairQ1.20.5.2-InventoryandCatalog\">Inventory and Catalog</h3><ul><li><p>Fixed a bug that caused a loading screen freeze when adding compatible parts and services to catalog items.</p></li><li><p>Rejecting an item on an Internal Purchase Order will no longer zero out the \u201cQuantity to ship\u201d fields of the page.</p></li></ul><h1 id=\"RepairQ1.20.5.2-Improvements\">Improvements</h1><ul><li><p>Concurrent appointment fields have been renamed \u201cMaximum Appts\u201d for clarity and consistent behavior across all available settings.</p></li><li><p>Test Mode batch delete errors have been fixed, and any deletion will be recorded in the System Log.</p></li><li><p>Once Test Mode has been turned off, it cannot be reactivated. This ensures data integrity after the Admin has decided to continue with regular business operations.</p></li><li><p>The Test Mode banner now has a clickable link to access Test Mode and Batch Delete settings.</p></li></ul>",
      "representation": "export_view",
